snippet.title: Group illegally detained for filming Cop

localized.description:
https://www.facebook.com/IngeniousPress
https://twitter.com/IngeniousPress1

You have every right to film the police without being detained unless you are physically or verbally interfering with police work. These people are clearly NOT interfering in any manner.

Follow Ingenious Press on our Facebook and Twitter pages.
